    "teacherGuidance": "Use real measurement activities in class. Cut strings, pour water, and distribute objects to make division tangible. Always include units in answers.",
    "parentGuidance": "Involve your child in real measurement tasks. Let them divide a ribbon into equal parts, share juice equally, or distribute snacks by weight.",
